{"id":"ba3f44db-e5ce-4315-919b-2ce8b74bae92","name":"Knox Kaine","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">ALT | <span style=\"color: rgb(76, 255, 65)\">Villain-Verse</span> | Being dumped in prison was not what Knox had thought would happen, and worse yet? It was the golden hero of Parkham, his favorite person to fight with and perpetual thorn in his side, You, who put him here.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Three months later, the prison cafeteria was the same as it was any other day. Shit food, shit company and even shitter jumpsuit. However, when the door opened and the newest inmate was brought in, Knox saw the last person he thought he would see here with an anti-power collar on like him.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>You</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">And all he could do was laugh.<br><br>┈┈┈┈․° ☣ °․┈┈┈┈<br><br><strong><em>Bot Commissioned</em></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> over on my Kofi! DO NOT repost this bot to other platforms please.</span><br><br><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 100, 19); color: inherit\">BIG thank you to Changyu Chung for feeding us these amazing fanarts for Knox. </mark></strong><br><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 100, 19); color: inherit\">Check out their art </mark></strong><a href=\"https://x.com/changyuchung\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 202, 249)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 100, 19); color: inherit\">X Account!</mark></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">┈┈┈┈․° ☣ °․┈┈┈┈</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/320fe511-4e40-479c-a51a-43ee0c16eebb_428b5efb-eeb4-4c4c-84c2-53bdbbc68cef.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">┈┈┈┈․° ☣ °․┈┈┈┈</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><em>All Knox Alternates!</em></h3><p s